  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple puzzle game perfect for lovers of casual play, logic challenges, and adorable cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to Play:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various shapes of panels are screwed to the wall. Just remove the colored screws and place them into matching-color boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless procedurally generated levels with gentle difficulty curves, ideal for quick sessions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two cute kittens watching your progress! (Sadly they can’t move yet, but maybe in the future!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More cats hidden in achievements waiting to be unlocked!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504140/extras/3163ac8c9d801d7c46359e07f954fc63.avif?t=1740073872\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple puzzle game perfect for lovers of casual play, logic challenges, and adorable cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to Play:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various shapes of panels are screwed to the wall. Just remove the colored screws and place them into matching-color boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless procedurally generated levels with gentle difficulty curves, ideal for quick sessions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two cute kittens watching your progress! (Sadly they can’t move yet, but maybe in the future!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More cats hidden in achievements waiting to be unlocked!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504140/extras/3163ac8c9d801d7c46359e07f954fc63.avif?t=1740073872\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p></li></ul>",
